Pretty decent, I’d say it’s on average better than the previous month. I also agree that momosawa one is exceptional, their best work to date if I do say so myself. Personally, I found the big names (chiguchi miri, Misao, EB110, etc), with the notable exception of Ookami Ou, to be the most lacking this edition; while the smaller names were exceptional: Momosawa Kyradain, Yuruchi, Airandou, and a few others really brought their A-game. Solid 6-7/10 from me, pending further “analysis”. Also holy shit, this was uploaded the night before November, fastest upload we’ve had so far, thank you kind stranger!
